 />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲特色:<br />\n開放久違的地獄/聖戰!!!<br />\n翅膀升級系統!!<br />\n最大特色 所有物品 都能打王就有了!!<br />\nGM舉辦活動極多 前所沒有!!<br />\n<br />\n開服後，將會出現以下活動，等您來領積分！<br />\n1.衝轉衝等活動<br />\n2.宣傳獎勵積分<br />\n3.如有玩家有任何活動意見,而又經GM接受跟採用,即可獲得100積分<br />\n將有更多活動陸續開放,敬請期待!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGM給玩家的承諾:<br />\n遊戲裡絕對不會出現親友團或GM團等情況,保證絕對公平公正。<br />\n此外本服絕對打擊遊戲騙案,嚴禁有玩家使用任何方法或途經騙取他人<br />\n帳號/金錢或遊戲物品<br />\n一經發現而又被查明屬實者,本服絕對嚴懲。<br />\n本服致力打造高質素的遊戲環境,<br />\n讓各位玩家可以享受愉快的遊戲,<br />\n沒有最好,只有更好。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲網頁:(7月3號就發出來)<br />\n論壇網頁:<a href=\"http://ourkop520.freebbs.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fourkop520.freebbs.tw&d=3kuNeJD51JJbiD%2FxdPUtNJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=a6b50b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ourkop520.freebbs.tw</a><br />\n遊戲帳號:solomonc"},{"pid":"f1fc7aa6baab1ff00f883bfc4b7899c9c28aa6d4","tid":305886,"uid":55231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"支持 童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0a9e3d17fe9f3c6ce4b5831cfc13ca8c073159","tid":305886,"uid":22621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"聽日開左AC留個名 加個好友一齊升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa69afa211cac05d048a1c210e6982f0afea23c","tid":305886,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aec954b03890e828281280e5a9138914d884f2","tid":305886,"uid":22621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"唔知玩狙定雙劍好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05873b9d5226899d9bc9415cd4604eda73023301","tid":